::: Pheniox took both blasts in the chest and fell to her side. Marine took 
out a large cannon gun :::

::: Gremlin, Jackle, and Balck Aracnia came on the scene followed by 
Transanulas :::

::: They all extended there firearms towrds the fuzor when Megatron entered 
:::

::: Megatron ::: Quickstrike! You have alot of explaining to do.....

::: Hell Beast roared from behinde him ::: Yes, and he can do it from inside 
the brig!

::: Gremlin and Jackle steped forward to collect him as Megatron frowned on 
the situation :::

::: Megatron ::: No, no. He will come with me to my chambers. I will talk to 
him.

::: Hell Beast, knowing full well he had complete survalience of Megatron's 
room, ::: Agreed. Take him.
